{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给君实的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给君实的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月12日）君实学兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来信收到。你是土改过程受打击的人，当此情况下，宜有以善处。生活困难，希望能就近获得适当解决。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"此复，顺颂康吉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五〇年五月十二日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"[1]君实，可能是傅君实。傅君实早年曾在湖南省立第一师范学校读书。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":12}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":380,"page_end":380},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}